        },
        {
            "text": "KLOE used [6] two angles method to describe \u03b7, \u03b7 \u2032 wave functions:",
            "section": "I. INTRODUCTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 7,
            "section_rank": 2,
            "ref_spans": [
