                    "text": "10]"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "To remove the mixing angle dependencies from kinematic factors and phase space the measurement is performed at t \u2032 = t \u2212 t min = 0",
            "section": "I. INTRODUCTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 2
        },
        {
            "text": "If the differential cross section parameters are the same, then R equal (7) or (8) depending from the beam particle type.",
            "section": "I. INTRODUCTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 2
        },
        {
            "text": "The results of the mixing angle measurements in \u03c0 \u2212 and K \u2212 beam for pseudoscalar mesons \u03b7, \u03b7 \u2032 are presented in our report. ",
            "section": "I. INTRODUCTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 2
