            "section": "II. GAMS-4\u03c0 SETUP AND EVENT SELECTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "The type of the beam particle is defined reliable by two threshold cherenkov counters [14] with quartz optics. ",
            "section": "II. GAMS-4\u03c0 SETUP AND EVENT SELECTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 3,
